snippet.title: Séculos - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Séculos is a short game, inspired by the quarentine period, where you have to find ways to pass your time by doing various activities around the house you're stuck in, while you wait for someone to come. The activities include light puzzles and minigames, which may lead to different endings.
